{
  "id": "S2P05302",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "PRINTER SETUP PANEL",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Some of the ways in which changing key functions or adding new"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "functions can make your editing faster and more efficient are listed"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "below:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Set up PF keys to execute frequently used commands in one"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "keystroke."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Rearrange keys (move functions from one key to another) to help"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "you remember the functions or reach the keys more easily."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Set a series of keys to perform related complex operations in"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "different ways depending on results of a previous operation. An"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "example of this is RFIND (PF5), RCHANGE (PF6)."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Create macro commands to perform arbitrarily complex operations and"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "assign them to PF keys."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+for next page)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
